raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"college_square_gardens\")
do social_post(\"naomi_intro\")
Mabel: Babe I'm dropping out!! 😭
Player: Babe what happened 😅
Player: U ok?
Mabel: NOOOOO!!!!
Mabel: It turns out that one of my sections was full and they slotted me into a section with no girls!! 🥹
- Lucky you! [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Lucky you!
	Mabel: Babe this is serious 😂
	Player: I know
	Player: There's a high likelihood of there being cute boys now 😤
	Mabel: Omg that's seriously the last thing on my mind 🥺
	Mabel: You're so silly 😆
- Is there a way to fix it?
	Player: Is there a way to fix it?
	Mabel: Apparently not! 
	Mabel: This is just their registration system rules...
	Mabel: I'll have to sit through history class with a bunch of boys now 🙂
Mabel: But I'm not too worried
Player: You sounded pretty worried though 😆
Mabel: Well I'm not worried becaaause
Mabel: I met my professor and she was so nice about the whole thing
Mabel: She said she'll let me sit up front and give me special attention hehe
Mabel: Look how pretty she is too!!
Mabel: img: suzanna/1
Mabel: I'm gonna sit up front and admire her the whole time hehe
- I'd do the same! [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: I'd do the same!
	Mabel: Babe omg 😆
	Mabel: No looking at any other girls please 🥰
	Player: I was just kidding
	Mabel: Besides she's a professor
	Mabel: I'm sure she's super busy all the time lol
- She seems lovely
	Player: She seems lovely
	Mabel: She really is!
	Mabel: She said she does what she can to support
Mabel: Thanks for listening to all my insecurities though ❤️
Player: Of course!
Mabel: Its so nice and sunny at least
Mabel: I won't let this ruin my day
Player: That's a good idea
Mabel: img: mabel/15
Mabel: Cute?
Player: For a top secret spy? A little too cute.
Mabel: It's all part of the disguise 😌
Mabel: 😂
Player: 😂
Mabel: This might be random but
Mabel: I love these simple moments with you
Mabel: Like nothing else really matters
Player: I love them too
Mabel: Just some silly jokes we keep telling each other for the past... 
Mabel: How many years has it been?
Player: A long time ❤️
Mabel: 🥰
Mabel: PinkThought: I hope it stays like this forever
Mabel: I promised mom I'd call her tonight so I'll talk to you in the tomorrow okay?
Player: No problem! Tell her I said hi
Mabel: Thanks partner ❤️
Mabel: PinkThought: Seriously you make my heart go all lovey dovey
Mabel: Talk to you tomorrow
Player: Nighty!
=> END"
